not ok 7 query aichat with simple validation and trace
# (in test file tests/integration/validation.sh, line 117)
#   `result=$(echo '{"query": "What is 2+2?"}' | aichat -r test-schema-demo -m ollama:llama3.1:latest --no-stream --trace)' failed with status 3
# Error: Unknown role `test-schema-demo`
not ok 8 query aichat with simple json validation and web search
