#   `result=$(echo "machine learning" |aichat -r data-discoverer -m ollama:llama3.1:latest --no-stream --trace)' failed with status 3
# Error: Preflight: role 'data-discoverer' requires tool calling but model 'ollama:llama3.1:latest' does not support it. Remove `use_tools` from the role or switch to a function-calling model.
